Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.46,0:00:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在的时代好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.97,0:00:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,终于能安心务农了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.18,0:00:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,红卫兵小将 你们好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.77,0:00:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毛主席万岁 打倒刘少奇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.67,0:00:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,国家主席都打倒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.16,0:00:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我算什么东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.82,0:00:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啪一下打下去 老实点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.58,0:00:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你还不老实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.63,0:00:56.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那时发觉身后有人在走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.64,0:01:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就赶快老老实实低头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.57,0:01:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但没人的时候自然会直起身来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.63,0:01:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,周恩来总理去世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.06,0:01:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就觉得国家失去了顶梁柱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.97,0:02:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn华文新魏\c&H00009C\fs35\shad4\pos(192,252)}民众口述中国动荡时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.97,0:02:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn华文新魏\c&H00009C\fs25\shad4\pos(192,273)}-跨越文化大革命-
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.49,0:02:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天的中国热气沸腾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.16,0:02:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现代化高楼鳞次栉比
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.64,0:02:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大街上车潮滚滚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.53,0:02:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在政治上维持社会主义体制的同时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.40,0:02:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中国大胆引入了市场经济
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.20,0:02:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,经济得到爆发性的成长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.23,0:02:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以至被称为世界的工厂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.02,0:02:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回想起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.06,0:02:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中国开始走上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.74,0:02:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,通向繁荣的改革开放路线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.98,0:03:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是在那场文化大革命结束后不久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.58,0:03:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跨越了文革才有了今天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.56,0:03:08.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很多人都有这种想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.70,0:03:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,持续了十年的文化大革命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.36,0:03:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把中国人卷入了激烈的漩涡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.97,0:03:22.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,极大改变了每一个人的人生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.92,0:03:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那场风暴中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.17,0:03:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人们经历了些什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.31,0:03:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想到了些什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.77,0:03:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又是如何行动的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.53,0:03:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,二十年来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.71,0:03:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一直在中国采访
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.03,0:03:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但文革在人们的心中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.75,0:03:42.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留下了深深的伤痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.75,0:03:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此在摄影机前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.40,0:03:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大都三缄其口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.25,0:03:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今年恰逢文革发动四十周年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.40,0:03:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对于自身所经历的苦难的时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.03,0:04:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人们终于开始开口了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.64,0:04:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们采访了四十多位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.83,0:04:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当时身处不同立场的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.55,0:04:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听他们长时间述说自己的人生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.87,0:04:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,将分为四集播出的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.05,0:04:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是民众所叙述的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.10,0:04:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中国动乱年代的详实纪录
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.60,0:04:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,故事从一九六六年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.64,0:04:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,红卫兵的诞生开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.76,0:04:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,红卫兵的诞生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.51,0:04:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一九六六年八月十八日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.75,0:04:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,北京天安门广场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.35,0:04:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,挤满了红卫兵等百万人的民众
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.46,0:05:04.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,庆祝毛泽东发动文化大革命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.66,0:05:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那时候下面人山人海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.64,0:05:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那种场面我生平第一次看见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.39,0:06:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,促使年轻大集会的起因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.55,0:06:24.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是某一个事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.36,0:06:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大会的三个月前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.72,0:06:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中国第一名门大学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.44,0:06:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,北京大学的校园里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.38,0:06:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贴出了一张大字报
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.15,0:06:38.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,张贴的是几个教师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.08,0:06:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,牛辉林先生当时是北大学生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.74,0:06:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他清楚记得当天的情形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.10,0:07:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大字报谴责校长及校党组织
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.67,0:07:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样写道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.31,0:07:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切革命的知识分子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.92,0:07:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是战斗的时候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.15,0:07:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,消灭一切修正主义分子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.38,0:07:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一个星期后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.12,0:08:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事态发生意外的变化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.16,0:08:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,党的机关报和电台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.35,0:08:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大肆报道党中央支持此大字报
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.63,0:08:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毛泽东提出造反有理的口号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.94,0:08:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,试图依靠群众运动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.30,0:08:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,清除掌握实权的势力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.20,0:08:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以把权利集中于自己手中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.88,0:08:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,造反有理这个口号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.28,0:08:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,改变了青年人对权力的看法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.73,0:08:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使之卷入狂热的漩涡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.62,0:09:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所谓红卫兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.70,0:09:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是宣誓效忠毛泽东
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.54,0:09:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,推动文革造反运动的急先锋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.50,0:09:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以初高中生和大学生为中心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.07,0:09:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,红卫兵组织迅速遍布全中国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.34,0:11:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是拍摄红卫兵上街行动的映像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.51,0:11:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,红卫兵以破四旧为口号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.86,0:11:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所谓四旧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.61,0:11:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是指旧的思想、文化、风俗和习惯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.41,0:11:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,红卫兵把路名和店名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.91,0:11:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,改成所谓革命性的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.54,0:11:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凡被认为是资产阶级的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.68,0:11:56.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,连人们的服装也要受到批判
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.00,0:12:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,破四旧还殃及历史文物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.05,0:12:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有西装肯定被没收
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.98,0:12:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有领带就没收领带
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.96,0:12:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那时候的皮鞋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.12,0:12:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是意大利名牌那种的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.56,0:13:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鞋头尖的就会被抄走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.50,0:13:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们冲进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.90,0:13:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不说话就乱砸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.14,0:13:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有些结实的东西砸不坏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.55,0:13:25.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就拼命砸直到砸坏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.64,0:14:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为防止红卫兵再来砸东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.56,0:14:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想了个办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.04,0:14:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是张贴毛主席语录
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.74,0:14:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这一来他们就没办法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.14,0:14:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为谁也不敢动毛主席语录
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.56,0:14:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,村民们就这样保护了很多文物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.95,0:14:34.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,文革开始的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.74,0:14:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想成为红卫兵是有条件的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.00,0:14:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是出身的阶级要好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.38,0:14:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当时作为国家政策
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.80,0:14:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把人们分成好坏两类阶级成分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.15,0:14:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阶级成分好的被称为红五类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.43,0:14:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,包括以前参加革命运动的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.29,0:15:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,共产党员和军人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.53,0:15:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及工人和贫穷农民等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.76,0:15:13.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而被认为出身不好的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.48,0:15:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,则称为黑五类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.33,0:15:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,包括以前的地主、富农
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.86,0:15:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及被认为对共产党革命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.47,0:15:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,持否定思想的反革命分子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.47,0:15:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,右派分子等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.56,0:15:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,红卫兵首先把攻击矛头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.11,0:15:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,指向黑五类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.69,0:15:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当时频繁地进行抄家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.30,0:15:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,定下目标就破门而入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.99,0:15:47.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,彻底搜寻反革命证据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.90,0:15:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没收家财
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.29,0:15:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,红卫兵的行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.23,0:15:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开始越来越暴力化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.75,0:18:50.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为死脑筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.58,0:18:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这些东西早扔掉就没事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.03,0:18:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但这是一辈子的血汗啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.90,0:19:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就藏在身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.22,0:19:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,红卫兵乒乒乓乓敲门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.87,0:19:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我妈没见过什么世面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.96,0:19:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把东西藏在身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.59,0:19:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一发抖全掉了出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.44,0:19:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人家不用抄就全拿走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.79,0:19:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她这里藏点那里藏点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.57,0:19:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抄家的一砸门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.28,0:19:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我妈逃到三楼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.57,0:19:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吓得全身发抖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.85,0:19:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说不得了 红卫兵来了呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.25,0:20:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每个人的出身阶级
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.59,0:20:18.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在建国后第二年开始设定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.55,0:20:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,农村和城市各自设定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.84,0:20:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,详细的阶级区分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.68,0:20:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一般财产越少阶级成分便越好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.83,0:20:31.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目的是把阶级斗争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.27,0:20:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作为建设国家的动力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.49,0:20:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,文革开始后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.90,0:20:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迫使人们强烈意识到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.10,0:20:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自身的阶级成分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.49,0:20:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阶级成分引发的歧视和迫害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.19,0:20:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,变本加厉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.12,0:20:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我家因为有点收入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.72,0:20:56.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,土改的时候被定为中农
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.13,0:21:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是村民们还是把你看作地主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.86,0:21:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要对你进行阶级斗争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.30,0:21:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然有影响
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.52,0:21:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,连我的儿子们都受到影响
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.68,0:21:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被定为小业主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.57,0:21:41.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我父母做生意时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.31,0:21:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有雇用人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.19,0:21:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,解放后凡有雇佣人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.02,0:21:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就被定为资本家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.65,0:21:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,短短十年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.52,0:21:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,私人经营犯了什么法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.44,0:21:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要把家里东西全抢光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.99,0:22:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,犯了什么法啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.99,0:22:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还要戴上了资本家的帽子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.35,0:22:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出身不好 是上中农
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.12,0:22:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再上去就是富裕中农
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.04,0:22:21.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要属于富农了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.02,0:22:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我家的这种情况下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.30,0:22:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出身不是贫下中农
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.51,0:22:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们说你能进入沪东造船厂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.20,0:22:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真不容易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.68,0:22:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这种人怎么能进国营企业
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.16,0:22:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,建造军舰的工厂工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:47.01,0:24:50.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出身不好而被视为黑五类的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.41,0:24:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被要求自我改造思想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:52.52,0:24:55.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,与自己的家人划清界限
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:57.41,0:25:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甘铁生先生便是其中之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:01.54,0:25:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由于他父亲在日中战争期间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:04.23,0:25:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当过日本军的翻译
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:42.92,0:26:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,年轻人开始相互竞争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:45.92,0:26:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对毛泽东的忠诚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:49.33,0:26:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,通过文化大革命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:50.89,0:26:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毛泽东名副其实地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:52.68,0:26:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站上了权利的顶峰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:56.24,0:26:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对毛泽东的个人崇拜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:59.00,0:27:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,急速上升
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:36.97,0:28:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,语录不贴又不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:41.48,0:28:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但要贴的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:44.02,0:28:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果错了一个标点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:49.74,0:28:55.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又会被无故恶打一顿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:49.67,0:29:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毛泽东为何要发动文革
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:54.72,0:29:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原因要追溯到某项政策的失败
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:59.73,0:30:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一九五八年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:01.89,0:30:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毛泽东提出要在十五年内赶超英国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:06.14,0:30:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,动员大众
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:07.74,0:30:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,实施快速扩大生产政策
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:11.19,0:30:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是所谓的大跃进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:21.97,0:30:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特别是钢铁增产被认为是关键
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:25.72,0:30:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,连农民也被动员起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:28.91,0:30:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,农村建造了原始的炼钢炉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:32.11,0:30:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,动用劳力从事炼钢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:37.44,0:30:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,农田被荒废
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:40.02,0:30:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,农地公有的人民公社制度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:43.12,0:30:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也使劳动积极性丧失殆尽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:46.60,0:30:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但成果却被夸大报道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:52.79,0:30:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我说弄点吃的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:56.34,0:30:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,烧点粥晚上吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:00.09,0:31:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们说没有锅子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:02.47,0:31:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那锅子哪里去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:04.38,0:31:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们说砸了拿去炼钢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:07.12,0:31:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就觉得怎么会这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:10.58,0:31:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只好踩车去厂里吃晚饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:19.04,0:31:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把木材、麦秆做燃料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:24.16,0:31:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用废钢铁炼钢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:30.28,0:31:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是火力不够
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:33.23,0:31:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本不能融化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:51.86,0:31:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都说共产党的好话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:54.72,0:31:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我不说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:56.54,0:31:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就说大炼钢铁错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:58.93,0:32:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是做傻事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:01.92,0:32:04.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把好好的钢搞坏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:05.39,0:32:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还要上报说是多出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:07.38,0:32:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,实际上是少掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:09.37,0:32:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我讲了我的观点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:11.62,0:32:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,结果坏事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:13.71,0:32:15.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,后来我被定为反革命分子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:15.54,0:32:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是因为这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:38.95,0:32:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到了十月棉花掉在地上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:44.48,0:32:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,田里土豆都冻住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:47.00,0:32:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不许农民收割
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:51.91,0:32:55.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,农民都很不满
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:56.01,0:32:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但什么也不敢说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:30.34,0:33:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那时候村干部虚报产量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:38.20,0:33:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说一块田收了一千五百公斤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:46.03,0:33:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么可能呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:48.46,0:33:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可要是你报得少就会挨揍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:31.41,0:34:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一发牢骚就给你扣帽子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:35.18,0:34:39.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说你破坏文革大好形势
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:39.34,0:34:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给社会主义脸上摸黑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:06.46,0:35:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有的村里死了好几十人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:14.63,0:35:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是可怕啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:37.28,0:35:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当时有个人去了农村视察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:41.43,0:35:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,彭德怀国防部长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:44.87,0:35:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,彭德怀目睹惨状大吃一惊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:48.38,0:35:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,致信毛泽东
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:55.36,0:36:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大炼钢铁运动浪费了资金和劳力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:01.38,0:36:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虚报产量之风盛行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:05.29,0:36:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,脱离现实便无法争取民众的支持
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:11.41,0:36:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毛泽东拒不接受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:14.90,0:36:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,视之为资产阶级反动思想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:17.84,0:36:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对彭德怀严加批判
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:21.98,0:36:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,彭德怀及其支持者被赶下台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:29.82,0:36:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但大跃进的失败是显而易见的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:34.74,0:36:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毛泽东被迫辞去国家主席一职
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:38.96,0:36:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一九五九年四月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:41.58,0:36:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刘少奇就任国家主席
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:47.56,0:36:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刘少奇为重整经济
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:51.04,0:36:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,着手有现实性的改革
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:57.35,0:36:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而支持他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:59.59,0:37:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是共产党总书记邓小平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:03.42,0:37:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刘少奇和邓小平修改了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:06.29,0:37:08.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不现实的钢铁产量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:12.39,0:37:17.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,并把部分农村农地归还个人所有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:17.32,0:37:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,准许自由市场买卖等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:19.96,0:37:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,实施了一系列
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:21.48,0:37:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,提高人们劳动积极性的政策
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:24.47,0:37:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,生产开始逐渐恢复
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:09.22,0:38:12.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刘少奇、邓小平等务实派的抬头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:12.74,0:38:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使毛泽东深感不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:16.47,0:38:18.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他认为他们的政策
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:18.74,0:38:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是向资本主义路线的倒退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:22.27,0:38:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,试图通过动员红卫兵等大众势力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:25.06,0:38:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以夺回实权
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:27.01,0:38:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,转变路线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:29.97,0:38:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这便是文化大革命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:39.12,0:38:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毛泽东的亲笔文章
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:42.54,0:38:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,炮打司令部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:46.53,0:38:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从中央到地方的某些领导同志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:49.12,0:38:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站在反动立场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:50.91,0:38:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,实行资产阶级专政
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:54.20,0:38:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,何其毒也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:58.13,0:39:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毛泽东的政治意图
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:00.32,0:39:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开始时不为人知
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:06.04,0:39:08.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁是革命的敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:09.14,0:39:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人们热衷于寻找身边的攻击对象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:14.24,0:39:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,与红卫兵对抗自然不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:16.77,0:39:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,连当旁观者都不允许
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:26.19,0:39:27.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,北京的学校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:27.72,0:39:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接连被红卫兵控制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:30.80,0:39:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同学、教师成了批判对象
